snippet.title: Fortune Street 2: Rolling Again Fan Mod Trailer
snippet.description:
Fortune Street was released for the first time across seas over ten years ago on the Wii, and hasn't again on consoles ever since. Now, Fortune Street is Rolling Again for its western fans in a package that provides a glimpse of what if it ever had a second, retooled experience.

This is a fan modification of Fortune Street that you can patch that is built for Dolphin Emulators. It adds brand new stages, remixes the rules, adds improvements to online functionality and more. This project took a year and a half to make, and wouldn't be possible without the huge help from the Fortune Street Modding Community. Updates to discovered bugs and balancing stages are sure to follow. I hope those who are able to patch this will have a great time, hopefully, even with some friends!

Check out more details about Fortune Street 2 with the link to the online guide below:
https://docs.google.com/document/d/1EhV7drz1v16NlwWSem1-SwgpBu9tWF8iYB0jLMKv3gU/edit?usp=sharing

Need help patching? Looking for online matches? Want to get the latest news on patch updates?
Check out the Fortune Street 2 Rolling Again discord server with this link:
https://discord.gg/aAeCzyeSSb

#fortunestreet #fanproject
